I"ô<p>We all need to record something now and then, be it a podcast, a tune youâ€™d like to listen to later, a meeting to review or a friend attempting to sing. One of the best ways to do this is the Voice Memos app, available for free on all Apple devices.</p>

<h1 id="homescreen">Homescreen</h1>
<p>The Voice Memos app is terribly simple. You get a title at the top, a search bar, a list of all your recordings and a big red button at the bottom.</p>

<div class="media multiple">
    
        <img src="/assets/foto/altro/lazyload.png" data-src="/assets/foto/articolo/memos/homescreen.jpg" alt="" class="lazyload" />
