<h1 id="conclusion">Conclusion</h1>
<p>Most current devices offer a recording app by default and Appleâ€™s Voice Memos app gets the job done via a simple but powerful interface full of useful features. Thatâ€™s why itâ€™s the most use voice recording app on all their platforms, and you should give it a try to see if itâ€™ll fit your recording needs.</p>

